      "pos": [
        10788,
        10803
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The next two sections demonstrate how you can deploy SQL Server VMs to Premium Storage.",
      "pos": [
        10805,
        10892
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "As mentioned before, you do not necessarily need to place the OS disk onto Premium storage.",
      "pos": [
        10893,
        10984
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "You might choose to do this if you are intending to place any intensive IO workloads on the OS VHD.",
      "pos": [
