      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Run the migration outside of Azure scheduled maintenance.",
      "pos": [
        32539,
        32596
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Ensure you have configured your cluster quorum correctly.",
      "pos": [
        32603,
