      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Then set the Possible owners of the IP Address resource to the migrated node, SQL2, and set this as OR dependency in the Network Name.",
      "pos": [
        33532,
        33666
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "See the ‘Adding IP Address Resource on Same Subnet’ section of the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Appendix<ept id=\"p1\">](#appendix-migrating-a-multisite-alwayson-cluster-to-premium-storage)</ept>.",
